OL,7,FA devastated mum has issued an
OL,8,Femotional appeal to help find her
OL,9,Fvulnerable son who desperately needs
OL,10,Fhis medication.
OL,12,FAndrew Heys, known as Andy, from , was
OL,13,Flast seen staying at his mother's
OL,14,Fhouse on Barton Lane, 11 March 2024.
OL,16,FAndy was due to attend an appointment
OL,17,Fthe next day, however, when his mother
OL,18,FJeanette Heys, went to check on him at
OL,19,F5:30am and realised he had disappeared.
