OL,7,FHis mother, who at first thought he
OL,8,Fhad gone for a walk, reported him
OL,9,Fmissing to the police when he still
OL,10,Fhad not returned, at around 8am.
OL,12,FAndy is 5ft 10 tall with a slim build.
OL,13,FHe is described as having mousey hair
OL,14,Fand hazel coloured eyes. He was
OL,15,Fwearing a dark green Craghoppers coat,
OL,16,Fblack joggers and navy blue Skechers
OL,17,Fshoes with a white sole. He could also
OL,18,Fbe carrying a black backpack.
