OL,5,Cmedication
OL,7,FAndy, described as "fit and sporty" by
OL,8,Fhis family, was diagnosed with Acute
OL,9,Fdisseminated encephalomyelitis in 2021.
OL,11,FThe condition left him paralysed and
OL,12,Fwas forced to leave his employment as
OL,13,Fwell as relearn how to walk and talk.
OL,15,FHis condition requires vital
OL,16,Fmedication, and his family want to
OL,17,Fraise awareness to his condition to
OL,18,Fhelp potential sightings. Andrew walks
OL,19,Fdistinctively, with his family saying
OL,20,F"people might think he is drunk".
